invalid type: string "7. Safety Warnings & Compliance\nDANGER: Never perform maintenance on a hot engine. Allow minimum 4-hour cooldown before\nborescope or physical inspection.\nWARNING: All sensor calibration must be performed using certified equipment traceable to NIST\nstandards. Uncalibrated sensors may produce false-normal readings masking critical faults.\n7.1 Regulatory Compliance\ns.\nn*¿